<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
  <title>Submission Processing Error - Support Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .header {
      color: #005ea2;
      font-size: 1.5em;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .content {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .error-details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      font-family: monospace;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="header">ECMPS Submission Error Notification - Support</div>
<div class="content">
  <p>Dear ECMPS Support Team,</p>
  <p>
    An error occurred while processing a submission.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Submission ID:</strong> {{submissionId}}<br>
    <strong>Configuration:</strong> {{configuration}}<br>
    <strong>User Email:</strong> {{userEmail}}<br>
    <strong>Error Reference ID:</strong> {{errorId}}
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Error Details:</strong>
  </p>
  <pre class="error-details">{{errorDetails}}</pre>
  <p>Please investigate this issue.</p>
  <p>Sincerely,</p>
  <p>Automated Notification System</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
